_sText:
I had this idea for a while and finally got around to it, this map consists of various stages from some of my favorite maps all merged into one, with no speed stops. Main map is 2min+ on a nofail run and the bonus is around a minute, both are very speedrun friendly. There were a lot of extra maps that I wanted to feature but there was just no place for them.

Main map consists of stages from: Sugarspeed, Verbena, Mentality, Flashbacks, Enlightened, Tumi, Terry, Relinquished, Askowo, Haunt, Accelerate, Bubblegum, Interstellar and Exiled.

Bonus consists of stages from: Hades, Poseidon, Aphrodite and Zeus.
